{"id":232145240,"title":"#微雷 #三年a班","content":"大家安安我是阿杰。\n不是很成熟的文章，不過就是想分享一下自己的一些感覺。\n\n今天看了3年A班，這好像是有點久的東西了，不過因為之前看過宇哥的講解，於是決定下午一次把它看完，看完只有兩個字，真爽。\n\n從一開始大家完全不信任老師，都只想著自己想著如何讓自己快點離開這個被囚禁的地方，到中間一些人講出了自己隱瞞的事，知道了自己的錯誤，然後大家一起合作完成老師想做的事情，真的讓人蠻感動的。\n\n看同學們的一些反應，還有在這部劇常常出現的，網路上的輿論，讓我想起了一首歌，《兇手不只一個》。\n\n而且我覺得就跟裡面說的一句話一樣，事情不能只看表面，裡面真的很多可以振奮人心的臺詞，是一部推薦大家去看的日劇。\n\n然後…柊一颯怎麼可以這麼帥啊?\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGd.jpg","excerpt":"大家安安我是阿杰。不是很成熟的文章，不過就是想分享一下自己的一些感覺。今天看了3年A班，這好像是有點久的東西了，不過因為之前看過宇哥的講解，於是決定下午一次把它看完，看完只有兩個字，真爽。從一開始大家","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"019a92bb-1305-4471-88dd-872c6ee60ce7","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-22T11:55:51.894Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-22T11:56:14.643Z","commentCount":42,"likeCount":172,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"日劇","forumAlias":"jp_drama","school":"菜鳥廚師阿杰","department":"tonykey125","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":170},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGd.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d7d54a33-80dd-4b71-8f95-7a5f6d3e9587","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGdl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGdl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGdl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-22T11:55:51.894Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-22T11:56:14.643Z"},{"id":"d7d54a33-80dd-4b71-8f95-7a5f6d3e9587","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGd.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/bKzmPGd","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bKzmPGdl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-22T11:55:51.894Z"